name: bimbostyleFourU (DeliberateV2)  - LORA
description:
This is model uses the exact same input as bimbostyleFour.

I was trained on deliberate_V2 which hopefully means that it's better applicable to other .ckpt in comparison to the normal "bimbostyleFour"

This lora is very responsive to body size prompts i.e. large breasts/wide hips/thick lips

And can also be used to bimbofie an existing model or lora

Combining this Lora together with One/Two/Three/Four in a "draw style" ckpt give great results and i can only recommend trying it out. (i don't know if the same applies to "real" ones as well)

can be mixed with every other bimbostyle

If you mix my models, i would recommend to always put the stronger weighted Lora in the front. i.e.

<lora:bimbostyleThree:0.5>:<lora:bimbostyleTwo:0.3>

Also i would go above a combined strength of 1 and from experience i would say .75-.9 is the sweet spot total strength

modelVersions.description:

It was trained on deliberate_V2 which hopefully means that it's better applicable to other .ckpt in comparison to the normal "Three"

Combining this Lora together with One/Two/Three in a "draw style" ckpt give interesting results show in the preview for example in pic 3 with lyriel and i can only recommend trying it out. (i don't know if the same applies to "real" ones as well)

If you mix my models, i would recommend to always put the stronger weighted Lora in the front. i.e.

<lora:bimbostyleFourU0.5>:<lora:bimbostyleThree:0.3>
